name: different constantpool order 1
description:
Two versions of `com.squareup.okhttp.Headers` in `okhttp-2.7.5.jar` built by the developer (Maven-Central) and by Google (GAOSS) respectivly. 
Both versions differ in the constant pool orders used by the binaries. See `https://github.com/binaryeq/bineq-study-supplementary/tree/main/mvnc-vs-gaoss/example3` for more info.
